    {
      "reviewerId": null,
      "reviewerUrl": null,
      "name": null,
      "reviewerNumberOfReviews": 2,
      "isLocalGuide": false,
      "reviewerPhotoUrl": null,
      "text": "家中老爸因病并发症导致下肢无力，近期在家中多次跌倒，家人工作繁忙无法提供全天候照护，我老妈也因照护压力而身心俱疲。\n\nAustinLoyal Care Centre的专业服务令人印象深刻。中心针对不同病患者提供专业的护理方案，包括个性化的物理治疗、血糖监测管理，以及适合的饮食安排。营养师还提供了有助于我老爸的补充建议，如Nutren、Prosure等。\n\n从入住手续到日常照护，每个环节都体现出专业水准，许多细节安排都超出预期。中心环境清洁舒适，护理人员专业耐心，对病人护理很有经验。探访时间安排合理，确保中心秩序井然。\n\n护理团队对饮食控制都很专业，创办人虽非医学出身，但在慢性病护理方面见解深刻。长辈在此接受照护后，情绪稳定，体力明显改善，跌倒情况完全消失。\n\n衷心感谢AustinLoyal Care Centre为我们家庭带来的专业照护和安心保障。谢谢你，Ms Lim，谢谢你为我科普了人生另一堂重要的课 - 如何好好照顾自家的老人和了解他们。",
      "textTranslated": "My father has lower limb weakness due to complications from his illness, and he's recently fallen several times at home. My family's busy schedules prevent him from providing full-time care, and my mother is also exhausted by the stress of caregiving.\n\nThe professional service at AustinLoyal Care Centre is truly impressive. The center offers specialized care plans tailored to individual patient needs, including personalized physical therapy, blood sugar monitoring, and a balanced diet. A nutritionist also recommended supplements like Nutren and Prosure that may be helpful for my father.\n\nFrom check-in to daily care, every aspect was professional, and many details went above and beyond. The center's environment is clean and comfortable, and the nursing staff are professional, patient, and experienced in patient care. Visiting times are well-planned, ensuring a well-organized center.\n\nThe nursing team is highly specialized in dietary management. Although the founder, while not a medical professional, possesses profound insights into chronic disease care. After receiving care here, my elder has experienced emotional stability, significant improvement in physical strength, and a complete cessation of falls.\n\nWe sincerely thank AustinLoyal Care Centre for the professional care and peace of mind it provides our family. Thank you, Ms Lim, for teaching me another important lesson in life - how to take good care of the elderly in your family and understand them.",
      "publishAt": "8 months ago",
      "publishedAtDate": "2025-09-02T07:46:14.961Z",
      "likesCount": 0,
      "reviewId": "Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxRFVrbHpjWEZUVms1UlZFWktNbmcwVkUxSmVHYxAB",
