      "rating": null,
      "responseFromOwnerDate": "2025-09-02T08:19:10.000Z",
      "responseFromOwnerText": "Dear Ms Yeo, \nThank you sincerely for your kind words and trust in AustinLoyal Care Centre. We are so glad to see your father’s progress, from improved strength to greater emotional stability and it means a lot to know our care has brought peace of mind to your family.\n\nOur team is truly grateful for your appreciation, and we will continue doing our best to provide comfort, dignity, and quality of life for every resident.",
